data.title: Phi Sigma Pi
data.meta_description: Phi Sigma Pi Center for Student Involvement | Phi Sigma Pi is a national Gender-inclusive honor fraternity based in the United States.
data.text:
Phi Sigma Pi is a national Gender-inclusive honor fraternity based in the United States. Phi Sigma Pi was founded with purpose of fostering the ideals of scholarship, leadership and fellowship. Phi Sigma Pi is organized into approximately one hundred and forty collegiate chapters at four-year collegiate institutions and several regionally established alumni chapters and associations serving approximately 53,000 brothers.

Phi Sigma Pi is a national Gender-inclusive honor fraternity based in the United States.
